So for one request we will send a Get Request then Service will return 302/303 with location attribute ( ie redirected with query param ) and as a response HTML with QueryString usually e1s1 is loaded. Sample proj is in this [link][2] and following is the change that is been implemented to avoid this default behaviour as following

